  "title": "Logistics Assistant [WCNH]",
  "description": "<p><p>Pick, check, and pack orders accurately to meet delivery schedules.</p></p><p><p>Perform <strong>goods receiving and dispatch duties</strong>, including loading and unloading of items.</p></p><p><p>Maintain a <strong>safe, tidy, and well-organized warehouse environment</strong> in accordance with <strong>5S and safety guidelines</strong>.</p></p><p><p>Support <strong>inventory accuracy</strong> through routine cycle counts and stocktaking exercises.</p></p><p><p>Comply with <strong>warehouse policies, procedures, and operational guidelines</strong> to ensure efficient daily operations.</p></p><p><p>Undertake additional <strong>warehouse or operational tasks</strong> as directed by the Supervisor or Assistant Manager.<br /></p><p>We regret only shortlisted candidates will be contacted. All applications will be handled confidentially. By submitting your application, you agree to the collection, use, retention, and disclosure of your personal information to prospective employers.</p><p>Wecruit Pte Ltd</p><p>EA License No: 20C0270</p></p>",
